<p class="indent3" style="-uslm-lc:I14" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">In the case of taxable years beginning after <date date="2017-12-31">December 31, 2017</date>, the Secretary shall adjust the $6,000 amount under clause (ii) at the same time and in the same manner as under section 415(d), except that the base period shall be the calendar quarter beginning <date date="2016-07-01">July 1, 2016</date>, and any increase under this paragraph that is not a multiple of $500 shall be rounded to the next lowest multiple of $500.</p>
